google_557.golden_query: SELECT CAST(SUM(IF(T2.Age > 65, 1, 0)) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(T1.Id) FROM posts AS T1 INNER JOIN users AS T2 ON T1.OwnerUserId = T2.Id WHERE T1.Score > 5
sparksql_query: SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN T2.Age > 65 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(T1.Id) FROM posts AS T1 INNER JOIN users AS T2 ON T1.OwnerUserId = T2.Id WHERE T1.Score > 5;
